room_title: Escape room "Locked Up" by Exithis in Mansfield
room_description: The guards have all responded to a fight in the mess hall. Now is your chance to break out and escape before you are put on death row. You are innocent, but there is only one way to prove it. You must escape before they return, use your logic and instincts to go undetected, and escape to freedom before it's too late.
